      "content": "i dont even know why i'm still doing this. the lab results came back again and it's just... nothing. another year of work down the drain. my funding is basically gone and i feel like i'm just a ghost moving through the halls. i’ve spent my whole life being this \"promising student\" and now there's nothing left. i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to exist in this loop. everything feels so heavy and i just want the weight to stop.",
